<lb n="0905b24"/>&CB00085;囉酤<note place="inline">引</note>計&CB00619;<note place="inline">引</note>室哩<note place="inline">二合</note>末底<note place="inline">四</note>崑拏&CB00619;<note place="inline">引五</note>
